{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/2022/02/17/macos-auto-capture-screen-for-time-tracking-2/","result":{"data":{"blog":{"id":"ce51df9e-4fd3-5a8a-b58f-9e58b7626d44","html":"<p>在上一篇文章 <a href=\"/macos-auto-capture-screen-for-time-tracking\">Mac 下通过自动周期截图来追溯每天的屏幕使用</a> 介绍了下一个简单的录屏脚本。这里做一个跟进，主要是以下两方面的内容：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>对原来脚本的修改，支持切换设备屏幕的情况</li>\n<li>提供 ffmpeg 命令可以把截图转换为 mp4 格式的视频</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"支持切换屏幕\" style=\"position:relative;\">支持切换屏幕<a href=\"#%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95\" aria-label=\"支持切换屏幕 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>我的工作电脑是一台 macbook pro ，在不同的场景下会使用不同的屏幕：在办公室会连接一台 LG 外接显示器，开会的时候会直接使用 macbook 的屏幕；而回到家可能会使用一台 Dell 的外接显示器。如果仅仅按照屏幕的序号截屏在图像的连续性上会差一些。不过幸好 mac os api 可以获取目前屏幕的更详细信息，我可以依据显示器型号记录信息。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token shebang important\">#!/bin/bash</span>\n\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/usr/local/bin:/usr/local/sbin:~/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin:/opt/homebrew/bin\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># use jq to get array length</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">result</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span>system_profiler SPDisplaysDataType -json<span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">screencount</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $result <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> jq <span class=\"token string\">'.SPDisplaysDataType[0].spdisplays_ndrvs | length'</span><span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># get current date</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">date</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">date</span> +%Y-%m-%d<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># create folder if not exists</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> -p <span class=\"token variable\">$date</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># get current date time with well format</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NOW</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">date</span> +<span class=\"token string\">\"%Y-%m-%d-%H-%M-%S\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># make screenshot</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">((</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>$screencount<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">))</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># get screen name</span>\n    <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">screenname</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $result <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> jq --raw-output <span class=\"token string\">\".SPDisplaysDataType[0].spdisplays_ndrvs[<span class=\"token variable\">$i</span>]._name\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># replace space with _</span>\n    <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">screenname</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">${screenname<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>_}</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># to lower case</span>\n    <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">screenname</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> -n $screenname <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">tr</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[:upper:]\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[:lower:]\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># use screen name to create file name</span>\n    screencapture -C -x -D <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$((</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token variable\">))</span></span> <span class=\"token variable\">$date</span>/screenshot-<span class=\"token variable\">$NOW</span>-of-<span class=\"token variable\">$screenname</span>.png\n<span class=\"token keyword\">done</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>如上所示，采用 screenname 作为文件名后缀可以保证截图的连续性。生成的文件就像如下这个样子：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 413px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fcac1d107758a7442fe4fb4bb0cc29e7/6c1e7/screenshot-with-screenname.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 130.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"screenshot with screenname\"\n        title=\"screenshot with screenname\"\n        src=\"/static/fcac1d107758a7442fe4fb4bb0cc29e7/6c1e7/screenshot-with-screenname.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fcac1d107758a7442fe4fb4bb0cc29e7/772e8/screenshot-with-screenname.png 200w,\n/static/fcac1d107758a7442fe4fb4bb0cc29e7/e17e5/screenshot-with-screenname.png 400w,\n/static/fcac1d107758a7442fe4fb4bb0cc29e7/6c1e7/screenshot-with-screenname.png 413w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 413px) 100vw, 413px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"使用-ffmpeg-生成视频\" style=\"position:relative;\">使用 ffmpeg 生成视频<a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-ffmpeg-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91\" aria-label=\"使用 ffmpeg 生成视频 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>截图一张张翻有两个坏处：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>需要自己一张张翻</li>\n<li>会占据更多存储空间，我这里一天最大的目录大小是 3G ，这里面很多截图是重复的，而众所周知，将这些图片如果以视频来存储可以充分利用视频的压缩算法，极大的降低所使用的存储空间</li>\n</ol>\n<p>既然只是为了 review 自己的工作，本来就是想要一个跑马灯的效果。这里我就简单搜索了下，可以用 <code>ffmpeg</code> 把截图按照时间顺序做成视频就好了。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ffmpeg <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -framerate <span class=\"token number\">15</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>                               <span class=\"token comment\"># 每秒 15 帧    </span>\n    -pattern_type glob -i <span class=\"token string\">'*dell_u2417h.png'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>    <span class=\"token comment\"># 指定截图文件的路径，dell_u2417h 是截图的屏幕名称</span>\n    -c:v libx264 <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>                                <span class=\"token comment\"># 指定视频编码器</span>\n    -pix_fmt yuv420p <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>                            <span class=\"token comment\"># 指定视频的像素格式，没事不用修改</span>\n    dell_u2417h.mp4                               <span class=\"token comment\"># 输出视频文件名，和截图的屏幕名称一直</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>用以上的命令，可以每个屏幕生成一个视频。</p>\n<h2 id=\"后续工作\" style=\"position:relative;\">后续工作<a href=\"#%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%AD%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" aria-label=\"后续工作 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>截屏目前做到了自动化，但是拼接视频没有做到自动化，需要手动拼接，可以考虑怎么做</li>\n<li>视频拼接目前是每个屏幕一个视频，如果能把屏幕按照时间线拼接起来会更好</li>\n</ol>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95\">支持切换屏幕</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-ffmpeg-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91\">使用 ffmpeg 生成视频</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%AD%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\">后续工作</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mac 下通过自动周期截图来追溯每天的屏幕使用-2","date":"February 27, 2022","tags":["自我量化","时间管理","mac","ffmpeg"]},"excerpt":"在上一篇文章 Mac 下通过自动周期截图来追溯每天的屏幕使用 介绍了下一个简单的录屏脚本。这里做一…"}},"pageContext":{"id":"ce51df9e-4fd3-5a8a-b58f-9e58b7626d44"}},"staticQueryHashes":["4202924991"]}